<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-253] Routerstat output needs correction</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-253</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The manual entry for routerstat, section 37.17, needs to be expanded to include the units for the output found under the &quot;Options&quot; section.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, the &quot;Description&quot; for Options S, R, F, D are reversed. The description for each is &lt;b&gt;_count/&lt;/b&gt;_length, whereas it should be &lt;b&gt;_length/&lt;/b&gt;_count. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adding sample output might be helpful.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
